msgid "In the Boot Menu, select your USB stick and press <strong>Enter</strong>."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <ol><li><p>
msgid ""
"If the computer starts on Tails, the Boot Loader appears and Tails starts "
"automatically after 4 seconds."
msgstr ""

