msgid ""
"If no Boot Menu appears or if your USB stick is not listed in the Boot Menu, "
"refer to the [[instructions on starting Tails using the Boot Menu "
"key|doc/first_steps/start/pc#boot-menu-key]]."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <ol><li><div><p>
msgid ""
"Starting the computer using a Boot Menu key can be faster than starting the "
"computer on Windows first and then on Tails. We recommend you learn how to "
"[[start Tails using the Boot Menu "
"key|doc/first_steps/start/pc#boot-menu-key]] if you use Tails regularly."
